{"word":"ταινιόω","slug":"ταινιόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ταινιόω</b></el> <el>(ταινιόω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ώσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ταινία'><el>ταινία</el></a>\n<p/><i>to bind with a head-band</i>, as a conqueror, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be crowned</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}